description:
BEYOND the DARKNESS returns with John Edmonds to the nexus of strange that is, The Stardust Ranch.

John tells us about the ranch he purchased that has reports of incredibly scary paranormal activity going on. Alien confrontations, molestation, demonic beings and large alien craft and beasts roaming the property. This location was later featured on Ghost Adventures with Darkness Dave on the investigation.
